fastformat::internal

fastformat::internal Namespace Reference

Detailed Description

Namespace within which internal FastFormat types and functions are defined.

Warning:
All entities defined within this namespace are subject to change without warning on any release, including revision releases.

All entities defined within any sub-namespace whose name begins with ximpl_ are subject to change without warning on any release, including revision releases.
